class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTrackElement\"><code>HTMLTrackElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLUListElement\"><code>HTMLUListElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLUnknownElement\"><code>HTMLUnknownElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLVideoElement\"><code>HTMLVideoElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HashChangeEvent\"><code>HashChangeEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/History\"><code>History</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Location\"><code>Location</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MessageChannel\"><code>MessageChannel</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/PageTransitionEvent\"><code>PageTransitionEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Plugin\"><code>Plugin</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PluginArray\"><code>PluginArray</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PopStateEvent\"><code>PopStateEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/PromiseRejectionEvent\"><code>PromiseRejectionEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RadioNodeList\"><code>RadioNodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ValidityState\"><code>ValidityState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><code>Audio()</code></strong> 构造器创建并返回一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLAudioElement\"><code>HTMLAudioElement</code></a>，可以将它附加到文档中以供用户交互，也可以用于管理和播放背景音乐。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: plain notranslate\">audioObj = new Audio(url);\n</pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"url\"><code>url</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">可选</span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>一个可选的、包含音频文件 URL 的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a>。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返回值","title":"返回值","isH3":true,"content":"<p>新创建的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLAudioElement\"><code>HTMLAudioElement</code></a> 对象，被设置为播放指定 <code>url</code>的音频文件。新对象的 <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此文档尚未被撰写，期待你的贡献!\"><code>preload</code></a> 属性被设置为 <code>auto</code> 且它的 <code>src</code> 属性被设置为具体的 URL 或 <code>null</code> （当没有提供 URL 时）。如果提供了 URL，浏览器在返回新对象之前开始异步加载媒体资源。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"使用备注","title":"使用备注","isH3":false,"content":"<p>你也可以使用其他元素创建方法，例如 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>document</code></a> 对象的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document/createElement\" title=\"createElement()\"><code>createElement()</code></a> 方法，去构建一个新的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLAudioElement\"><code>HTMLAudioElement</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"检测回放时机","title":"检测回放时机","isH3":true,"content":"<p>提供三种方法给开发者，判断音频文件是否已经加载，允许开始回放：</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>检测 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/readyState\" title=\"readyState\"><code>readyState</code></a> 属性的值. 如果值是 <code>HTMLMediaElement.HAVE_FUTURE_DATA</code>，说明有足够的数据开始回放并能至少播放一小段时间。如果值是 <code>HTMLMediaElement.HAVE_ENOUGH_DATA</code>，根据当前的下载速率，说明有足够的数据，你可以无干扰地播放至结束。</li>\n  <li>监听 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/canplay_event\" title=\"canplay\"><code>canplay</code></a> 事件。当足够的音频数据被发送至 <code>&lt;audio&gt;</code> 元素，能开始回放，即使可能出现中断时，会触发该事件。</li>\n  <li>监听 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/canplaythrough_event\" title=\"canplaythrough\"><code>canplaythrough</code></a> 事件。当音频应该没有干扰能够顺利播放时将会触发该事件。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>基于事件的方法是最优的：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>myAudioElement<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"canplaythrough\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">event</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">/* 音频可以播放；如果权限允许则播放 */</span>\n  myAudioElement<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">play</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"内存使用与管理","title":"内存使用与管理","isH3":true,"content":"<p>如果所有使用 <code>Audio()</code> 构造函数创建的 audio 元素被删除，根据 JavaScript 垃圾回收机制，如果播放正在进行，内存中的 audio 元素不会被移除。相反，音频将会继续播放并且它的对象会保留在内存中，直到播放结束或是被暂停（例如调用 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/pause\" title=\"pause()\"><code>pause()</code></a>）。在那个时候，这个对象才会成为垃圾回收的目标。</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/media.html#dom-audio-dev","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.HTMLAudioElement.Audio"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.HTMLAudioElement.Audio","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLAudioElement/Audio/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>The compatibility table on this page is generated from structured data. If you'd like to contribute to the data, please check out <a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data</a> and send us a pull request.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Media\">Web media technologies</a></li>\n  <li>实现了此接口的 HTML 元素：<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/audio\"><code>&lt;audio&gt;</code></a>。</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"使用备注","id":"使用备注"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"Audio() 构造器创建并返回一个 HTMLAudioElement，可以将它附加到文档中以供用户交互，也可以用于管理和播放背景音乐。","popularity":0.0005,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Audio()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Audio()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/htmlaudioelement/audio","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/htmlaudioelement/audio/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLAudioElement","title":"HTMLAudioElement"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLAudioElement/Audio","title":"Audio()"}],"pageTitle":"Audio() - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}